The Importance of Manual Testing
Manual testing plays a vital role in identifying bugs, usability issues, and performance gaps that automated tools might overlook. Unlike automation, manual testing incorporates human insight, ensuring a better understanding of user behavior and real-world functionality. At GT Infotech, our QA experts follow structured test cases to assess software performance, interface design, and overall reliability.

Comprehensive Quality Assurance Services
